  <metadata>
    <name>Col du Tourmalet (France)</name>
    <desc>France · 19.0 km · +1404 m · 7.4% avg. The highest paved pass in the central Pyrenees and the Tour's most-climbed col, from Luz-Saint-Sauveur. Approximate geometry anchored at the real trailhead for indoor training, not the exact road.</desc>
